Hello, I am a new client on Newsbreak and I have attended the webinar by Voluum. How do I claim the $500 bonus ad credits?

Hello! To claim your $500 bonus ad credits on NewsBreak, you'll need to follow the redemption process for ad credits. Here's a step-by-step guide:
1. Create an account on NewsBreak if you haven't already.
2. Once logged in, navigate to the billing section.
3. Select the Prepay option where you can add credits to your account.
4. Enter the promo code or details provided during the Voluum webinar to redeem your bonus credits.
If you have any issues or need further assistance, feel free to reach out!
For more detailed instructions, you can check out this article: [How to redeem a NewsBreak ad credit](https://help.newsbreak.com/hc/en-us/articles/17391456255629-How-to-redeem-a-NewsBreak-ad-credit).
